= Strengthening Unions

The unionization rate of American workers used to be very high, yet 40 years of neoliberal rule has caused immense harm to union power and unionization rates. We can attempt to once again strengthen unions.

- @investigate_union_busting: Aggressively pursue cases against union busting
- @resources: Use our party resources to support our allies.
- @bring_down: Instead, we will bring down the government with a no-confidence vote, and call for new elections.
- @no_change: Take none of these actions.
- @easy_discard


